Description: A modern, minimalist, privacy-focused web browser for Linux
 Open Browser is a fast and clean web browser built on GTK4 and WebKitGTK.
 It provides a distraction-free interface with strong privacy defaults:
 built-in ad blocking, tracker protection, HTTPS upgrades, and no telemetry.
 .
 Features:
  - Clean GTK4 native interface
  - Full tab management with keyboard shortcuts
  - Integrated ad and tracker blocker
  - Password manager backed by the system keyring
  - Bookmark and history management
  - Download manager with pause/resume
  - Private browsing mode
  - Hardware-accelerated rendering
